name: CSP's visual style reference
body:
### Welcome to CSP's aesthetics site
This page is intended to serve as a visual style reference for CSP. 

### Authors and Contributors
Please make contributions using [GitHub Flavored Markdown](https://guides.github.com/features/mastering-markdown/). You can check out the new `gh-pages` branch locally.

You can @mention a GitHub username to generate a link to their profile. The resulting `<a>` element will link to the contributor’s GitHub Profile. For example: Luke Zachmann (@lzachmann) created the first draft of this page online using GitHub.  

### Support or Contact
Having trouble? Check out GitHub's [documentation](https://help.github.com/pages) or contact CSP (<info@csp-inc.org>) and we’ll help you sort it out.
